'No good trying anything while that things conscious, best get her to
sleep, lets just hope it's spark like every others,' he thought to
himself.  He typed away again entering the commands to initiate an
override stasis lock.  At the same time he felt he would need
authorization to continue on any further, or if the stasis lock failed.

Kenzo walked over to the inter ship communications consul.
"Med Bay to command bridge, I have a situation here, I need to speak
to Rodimus Prime."
